data.name: ReadEmployment
data.value: select top(1) IDENTIFIER, LAST_QTR_INCOME, LAST_QTR, LAST_QTR_YR, SECOND_QTR_INCOME, SECOND_QTR, SECOND_QTR_YR, THIRD_QTR_INCOME, THIRD_QTR, THIRD_QTR_YR, FOURTH_QTR_INCOME, FOURTH_QTR, FOURTH_QTR_YR, SENT_DT, LAST_UPDATED_TMST, LAST_UPDATED_BY, CSP_I_NUMBER, WORKER_ID from CKT_INCOME_SOURCE where IDENTIFIER = @identifier

data.name: UpdateEmployment
data.value: update CKT_INCOME_SOURCE set LAST_QTR_INCOME = @lastQtrIncome, LAST_QTR = @lastQtr, LAST_QTR_YR = @lastQtrYr, SECOND_QTR_INCOME = @secondQtrIncome, SECOND_QTR = @secondQtr, SECOND_QTR_YR = @secondQtrYr, THIRD_QTR_INCOME = @thirdQtrIncome, THIRD_QTR = @thirdQtr, THIRD_QTR_YR = @thirdQtrYr, FOURTH_QTR_INCOME = @fourthQtrIncome, FOURTH_QTR = @fourthQtr, FOURTH_QTR_YR = @fourthQtrYr, LAST_UPDATED_TMST = @lastUpdatedTmst, LAST_UPDATED_BY = @lastUpdatedBy, WORKER_ID = @workerId where (IDENTIFIER = @identifier) and (CSP_I_NUMBER = @cspINumber)
